    "Data filtering is the process of screening and cleaning the data obtained during the data collection stage, with the primary goal of improving data quality.",
    "It can be accomplished through model-based methods or heuristic-based methods.",
    "Model-based methods.",
    "The methods filter low-quality data by training screening models.",
    "High-quality pre-training corpora can be used as positive samples, with the contaminated text to be filtered as negative samples, to train classifiers for filtering."
